Text: It was a pleasureMrSkilling I joined Enron Energy Services several years ago as General Manager of Major AccountsMid Atlantic region I have had the pleasure to meet you several times particularly at several republican fund raising breakfasts I believe Enron is a great company and destined for great things in the future As of it will be the last day of my employment with EES I wanted to say it was a pleasure working for you and I enjoyed the challenges we faced and the accomplishments we have made at EES over the last couple of years I hope in the future we can visit if your in the Philadelphia area or if I can be of assistance in anyway please dont hesitate to call Best Regards Frank LeMaster Inverness Court Chadds Ford PA Tel
